Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.38,0:00:42.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,都腫成這樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.49,0:00:44.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我記得還有…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.41,0:00:47.61,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.50,0:01:08.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好厲害 已經會彈了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.67,0:01:09.61,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.61,0:01:10.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,能彈完整的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.62,0:01:13.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,還… 還要練呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.50,0:01:17.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,對了 我們要演奏什麼歌
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我有好幾首合適的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.98,0:01:21.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,《春日影》不就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,只用來練習倒是可以…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,什麼叫只用來練習
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.37,0:01:32.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.62,0:01:34.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,歌詞？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,難道是新歌？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是愛音讓我寫的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳真的寫了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怪不得啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,給我看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.70,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,正適合初次Live演奏吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.41,0:01:52.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,給我看看啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是我叫她寫的 應該有權利看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.70,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.70,0:02:01.18,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這是小燈為我們寫的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,全新的我們的歌
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.63,0:02:06.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我來作曲
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.35,0:02:14.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希 妳還會作曲嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.70,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,雖然還在學 但燈都寫好詞了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我來吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.13,0:04:01.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我要和立希她們一起上RiNG的Live了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.77,0:04:10.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,等Live結束後 我再來邀請妳加入樂隊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.71,0:04:17.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,今天回家路上我想去找小祥聊聊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.37,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳要一起去嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.01,0:04:23.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我不去
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.14,0:04:28.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,今天應該不是妳練鋼琴的日子吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我的手很疼嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我就貼上了創可貼 但彈起吉他來好滑
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.09,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我去學了一下手指的柔軟操
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.09,0:05:34.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,據說只要跟著做手指就會變強
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我就想著盡量跟著做
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,爽世同學
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我來這附近有點事…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳原來在等我們啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,去練習吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳給我推薦的香薰 讓人放鬆的效果太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.59,0:05:53.67,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不錯 彈得很棒嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,咦 立希 妳還去換了衣服嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我沒去
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.92,0:06:08.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒上課？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不良少女啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我作了曲
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這麼快 真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希 好厲害
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.65,0:06:16.55,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,聽嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,非常好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,真的作好曲了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,燈 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,很溫暖
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,意思是很好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,話說…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,能不能節奏再放慢一點呀
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,要的就是那種衝刺感
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,行了 我發妳樂譜
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳這上面什麼都沒寫啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不是寫了和弦嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,之後聽著聲音演奏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.29,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒有表示怎麼按的東西嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳是說指法譜吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希 能用電腦做出來嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.38,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒有那個我彈不了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,在呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,流浪貓
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,開始樂隊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.67,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒有妳的部份
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒事 開始
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我把這段加上 重做一下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,流浪貓 妳每天都過來
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,到月底為止 每天都可以預約同樣的時間嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.26,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.26,0:08:30.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,給妳加上學生優惠 早期優惠 員工優惠
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.85,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,很努力嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,真的每天都約上了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,該加油了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,燈
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,來吃櫻桃了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,燈？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.93,0:08:56.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳已經足夠努力了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,就算踉蹌跌倒
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.19,0:09:03.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,還是爬起身 來到了這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,接下來實際練習一下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.07,0:09:09.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,6弦 上下 上下
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,5弦 上下 上下
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.19,0:09:16.38,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,4弦 上下 上下
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.37,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,3弦…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沿著海岸能看到的這種地形
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.18,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,叫做海岸階地
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,比較有名的地點有北海道的日高地區
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.79,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,三陸海岸北部 四國的室戶岬
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.86,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,三角同學 差不多到點了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.19,0:09:48.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.06,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.38,0:09:58.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,接下來講解它與河岸階地的區別
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那傢伙為什麼不來
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.84,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,儘管跟她說了每天都有
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,開始練習吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,要按照妳今早發給我的彈吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我重新想下編曲
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,練習怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.60,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.93,0:10:34.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這裡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這樣改怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,遲到了十分鐘
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.60,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,快點 她要生氣了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,等下 愛音
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.29,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們值日
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,到底來不來 能不能提前說一聲
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 來了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.30,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不是問這個
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.53,0:11:18.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳來之前 如果能說一聲就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.93,0:11:21.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,給我？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,把妳加進群了 以後記得來
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不許遲到
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,燈 開始練習吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.21,0:11:41.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,該看哪張樂譜
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.71,0:11:44.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,昨天的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,自己練到練會為止
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,大家一起來吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不開始嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.73,0:12:01.55,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.05,0:12:04.74,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,行嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.05,0:12:24.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,滿足
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,等下 還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,大家根本沒合上
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.60,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.30,0:12:35.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,樂奈不練也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那妳呢 妳好好練了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我在練呀
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳比以前彈得差了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,可是我很努力呀
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,大家配合不起來 算什麼樂隊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙也完全不行
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,比別人多練一倍
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我倒是會練…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.77,0:12:55.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,跑了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.69,0:12:58.26,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,真的像貓一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,根本沒有正經的練習
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,還是不要流浪貓了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,還是說…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不能保證她會來Live
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.82,0:13:23.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,如果再修改樂譜 就不是新手能彈的了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我一定會寫出配得上燈的歌詞的曲
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,有什麼想法都告訴我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這是我身為作曲的責任
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,為何事到如今…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,她是什麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,今天又來了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,爽世正在組樂隊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,她也邀請了我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是在嘲諷我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,真是越想躲開 對方越要湊過來
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,有必要跟她說清楚了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.59,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,要來月之森嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.43,0:14:24.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,Live當天 應該能見到她
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒來？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,可能跟之前一樣 只是遲到吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.91,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這裡彈錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.61,0:14:54.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,別吼我啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.26,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我每次來妳都改
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我試著彈 妳就只會無視或者說我不行
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.93,0:15:07.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,能不能為別人著想一點啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.05,0:15:07.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我還想說呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.91,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳們都冷靜一點
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.35,0:15:14.06,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,畢竟立希是現在最努力的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,別這麼說
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,各種事都交給了妳 真抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我有什麼可以做的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,有什麼事可以幫妳嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.58,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,大家一起 就能做好了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,意思是我靠不住嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我做不到像祥子那樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.92,0:15:44.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希太勉強自己了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,也對啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒有大家的話…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,下一站是鬼子母神前 鬼子母神前
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,可前往千歲橋教育會館
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,姐姐和祥子都能做到
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼我卻…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.74,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不行 她不接
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,流浪貓倒是和平常一樣不來
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不過 事情剛過不久 她確實不太好來
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我對她發了火
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,但的確各種事情都交給她做了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.13,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,大家不在一起還是不行
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我去找她
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不去妳的樂隊嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,心情不好就會變安靜 挺好
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.61,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我還要去樂隊 先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.53,0:18:04.11,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我因為樂隊的事這麼沮喪 妳還跟我說這個
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,能為了自己的樂隊而煩惱
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,也讓我有點羨慕
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼慢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.92,0:19:09.54,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我們等了2小時56分31秒
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,立希
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.55,0:19:13.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,跑了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.89,0:19:14.80,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,愛音
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,別跑
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,愛… 愛音…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.81,0:19:39.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,鞋子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.62,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳別跑
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我沒跑
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.09,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是妳非要追我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那妳停下
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我憑什麼聽妳的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不對 妳這是非法入侵
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,一點也不沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.94,0:19:59.67,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,就算被抓住寫個檢討就好
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.03,0:20:00.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我很擅長寫作文的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.74,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不是不怕被抓住嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.74,0:20:05.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳好煩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那是最終手段
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.46,0:20:10.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,只要妳站住 就都解決了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.44,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,誰會停下等妳啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,那我就一直追
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳真的好煩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,燈
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.34,0:20:30.89,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,抓住妳…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,出血了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這是海洋生物系列第6彈
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.90,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,珊瑚礁鬼蝠魟
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.77,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,翻車魚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.77,0:20:44.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,皇帶魚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.91,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,鯨鯊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.81,0:20:49.59,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這是藍鯨和長鬚鯨
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳笑什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,因為超可愛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.28,0:21:00.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,燈當然可愛了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,明天就是Live了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,已經無處可逃了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.70,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我的呢 我的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.81,0:21:17.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.65,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳應該還有什麼話該對我說吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳指什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,比如「謝謝」「謝謝」還有「謝謝」
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.43,0:21:25.81,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,憑啥
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,妳 怎麼在這
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,在和貓玩
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好長的貓
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不對 妳是我們學校初中的？
